comfort 1.0.0 API

Packages 
Package Description
de.ugoe.cs.comfort
Main package that includes utils classes as well as the main.
de.ugoe.cs.comfort.annotations
All annotations that are needed for this framework.
de.ugoe.cs.comfort.collection
Includes all parts that are needed for collecting metrics (data loader, data filter, data metric collector)
de.ugoe.cs.comfort.collection.filter
Includes all filters of the comfort framework.
de.ugoe.cs.comfort.collection.loader
Includes all loader of the comfort framework.
de.ugoe.cs.comfort.collection.loader.callgraph
Includes helper classes for de.ugoe.cs.comfort.collection.loader.CallGraphLoader
de.ugoe.cs.comfort.collection.loader.testcoverage
Includes helper classes for de.ugoe.cs.comfort.collection.loader.TestCoverageLoader
de.ugoe.cs.comfort.collection.metriccollector
Includes all metric collectors that are part of the framework.
de.ugoe.cs.comfort.collection.metriccollector.mutation
Classes that are used for the MutationDataCollector.
de.ugoe.cs.comfort.collection.metriccollector.mutation.executors
Executors that are used to execute a certain mutation testing framework
de.ugoe.cs.comfort.collection.metriccollector.mutation.operators
Operators that are applied to files in which mutations are integrated to simulate the mutant.
de.ugoe.cs.comfort.collection.metriccollector.parsing
Classes that are used for parsing an AST.
de.ugoe.cs.comfort.configuration
Includes models for the configuration.
de.ugoe.cs.comfort.data
Includes all classes that represent loaded data
de.ugoe.cs.comfort.data.graphs
Includes all graph type classes in which data is stored (e.g., call graphs).
de.ugoe.cs.comfort.data.models
Includes all models which are created from the underlying data (e.g., a model that represents a Java class)
de.ugoe.cs.comfort.database.models
Includes all needed database models to access a MongoDB.
de.ugoe.cs.comfort.exception
Includes all custom exceptions that are needed.
de.ugoe.cs.comfort.filer
Includes all filer.
de.ugoe.cs.comfort.filer.models
Includes all models used for filers.
